original_title: Saturday Night Live: The Best of Dana Carvey
overview: From 1986 to 1993 Dana Carvey dominated the stage at Saturday Night Live with dead-on impressions and some of the most popular characters in SNL history.  See the best of the Church Lady, Hans and Franz, George Bush, Ross Perot, Sassive Headwound Harry, Wayne's World and many others. Plus there's extra material, including Dana's favorite scenes that were cut after Dress Rehearsal and never seen before now.
tagline: Saturday Night Live: Best of Dana Carvey
title: Saturday Night Live: The Best of Dana Carvey
